#. Tag: title
#: man-checkXML6.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: man-checkXML6.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>checkXML6</command> is a tool to check for syntax errors in &kde; "
"DocBook &XML; files. It can also be used for other DocBook based &XML; "
"files, but you should use the less specific xmllint(1) tool if you are not "
"writing or otherwise working on &kde; documentation."
msgstr ""
"<command>checkXML6</command> je orodje za preverjanje sintaktičnih napak v "
"datotekah &kde; DocBook &XML;. Uporablja se lahko tudi za druge datoteke "
"&XML;, ki temeljijo na DocBooku, vendar morate uporabiti manj specifično "
"orodje xmllint(1), če ne pišete ali kako drugače delate na dokumentaciji "
"&kde;."

